oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gary Stewart interview - Joe Suglia - WBUK
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of an interview with Gary Stewart (performer), conducted by Joe Suglia on radio station WBUK.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Joe Suglia briefs Gary Stewart on the interview -- Joe Suglia introduces Gary Stewart -- Stewart talks about this being his first time at Wings Stadium in Kalamazoo -- Stewart talks about being from Kentucky, then moving to Florida, then to Nashville, and finally back to Ft. Pierce, Florida -- Stewart talks about playing with Charlie Pride's band -- Stewart talks about I See The Want To In Your Eyes -- Stewart talks about how hard it is for a new artist to get radio play -- Stewart talks about his latest He's Acting Single And I'm Drinking Double -- Joe Suglia concludes the interview
